<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hoş Geldin!</title>
    <style>
        /* Sitenin genel görünümü */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Orta kısımdaki kutu */
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.37);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #764ba2;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Merhaba! 👋</h1>
        <p>Web sitemize hoş geldin. Senin için buradayız!</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Keşfetmeye Başla</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
